## **TRACK** All Files Or Directories Listed Immediately Below

### An Alternative way to look at this is: Do **NOT** Ignore (i.e. TRACK!) Files Or Directories Listed Immediately Below

### **Files to track:**

# Thie below line is for guidance only. Remove as desired.
#!tracked-file-example.env

!.gitignore
!index.html
!README.md
!script.js
!style.css

### **Directories to track:**

# Thie below line is for guidance only. Remove as desired.
#!*/tracked-directory-example/

!/blog/*
!/css/*
!/js/*
!/page/*
!/pic/*
!/tool/*


